    "description": "Mikikogyo Co., Ltd. engages in construction business in Japan. The company operates through Construction Business, Housing Business, and Other Business segments. The company undertakes construction works for public facilities, commercial facilities, condominiums, apartment buildings, offices, warehouses, as well as public and private buildings; renewal works that includes partial repairs of exterior walls and interiors, and buildings renovation. It also offers gas installation works, such as pipe laying, road restoration, maintain and management works, pipeline construction, on-site construction, gas pipe maintenance work, and emergency security work; and firefighting equipment, such as sprinklers for buildings. In addition, the company undertakes facility constructions comprising installation of piping and equipment necessary for air conditioning, ventilation, and water supply and drainage, as well as offers inspection, cleaning, and part replacement of installed equipment services. Additionally, it undertakes civil engineering constructions for bridges, rivers, water supply, sewage, parks, squares, and the roadways. Further, the company engages in the installation, maintenance and management, and selling electricity through solar and wind projects; non-life insurance agency business; rental and management of real estate properties; food and beverage business; and steel and sheet processing. The company was founded in 1952 and is headquartered in Himeji, Japan."
